wiki.summary: On “DTB 4 Life,“ A Boogie drops multiple references calling back to his 2016 track “D.T.B. (Interlude)," a track in which A Boogie can’t trust his women: I love money, I don’t love bitches Fuck bitches, D.T.B., no, I don’t trust bitches Struggles in past relationships have left him distrusting them, leaving him lonely and troubled. Throughout the track, A Boogie also touches on his life of crime prior to the fame and reminisces about his friends and their fight with life in the unforgiving streets. Read more on Last.fm.
